name: RegisterWithInvalidData
descriptionHtml:
### Endpoint for registering the Admin:

Request payload must contain the following fields:

username: STRING,
password: STRING,
full_name: STRING,
role: STRING,
team_id: STRING,
data_of_birth: STRING ( format: "yyyy-mm-dd" ),
organization_name: STRING
qualification: STRING,
created_by: NUMBER ( format: 11 characters ),
city: STRING,
district: STRING,
state: STRING,
country: STRING,

Request:

POST - https://apiqa.inquitech.in/api/v1/admins/register

raw 
  {
    "username": "",
    "full_name": "",
    "password": "",
    "role": "",
    "team_id": "",
    "date_of_birth": "1989-06-20",
    "qualification": "bs.c",
    "city": "hyderabad",
    "district": "somehthing",
    "state": "tg",
    "country": "bs.c",
    "created_by": 1236547899
}

Response:

406 - Not Acceptable 

  {"status":406,"status_type":"error","message":"Role can not be null/empty","count":null,"data":null}
